  <sections xmi:id="_oTkP4C2DEd2K9MXQfaLjRA" name="Submit the change request" guid="_oTkP4C2DEd2K9MXQfaLjRA">
    <sectionDescription>Submit the change request through the proper channels to ensure compliance with the established change request management&#xD;
process. The technique will vary depending on the tools used to manage change requests.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <purpose>This task logs a requested change. Change requests may include requests for new features, enhancements, corrections,&#xD;
changed requirements, and so on. Any role may submit a change request as part of any task throughout the project lifecycle.</purpose>
